title: The Journal of Sir Walter Scott; From the Original Manuscript at Abbotsford
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: We passed through Lochore,but without stopping, and saw on the road eastward, two or three places,as Balbedie, Strathendry, and some others known to me by name.
